Put detailed information about all extra credit enhancements here.  

Pressing the T key will teleport the ship to a random location on screen if the ship is not null. (2)

Passing a level will add a life, up to a maximum of 5. (2)

At the end of a game user is asked for initials and their score is recorded. Scores are persistent across multiple games
	and the top 5 scores are displayed at the end of a game. (16)
	
Objects on screen with special powers using powerup Class (extra lives, powerups for ammo, etc) (8)

Ship doesn't spawn until it is safe from collisions (6)

Game statistics displayed on playing surface (4)

Bonuses for good game play (4)

Can use mouse to play game?